Package com.day.cq.dam.indd

Interface PageComponent

  • public interface PageComponent
    This interface defines a type for a page component.

    A PageComponent is a generic representation of wcm component. It consists of a resource type and properties to describe a component. Resource type and properties are specific for a certain component.

    Further, PageComponents can be nested.

    This interface must not be implemented by clients.

    Since:
    5.5
